_sText: **Jeesh the trouble fixing up shadowing in this map.. :) Playing takes place indoors in a wooden like fortress if you will. Personally made sure this is a 1st class map!** **Chose of bunny hop, knife and easy shotgun pwning at the end.** - Over 40 spawn points - Consits 21 traps overall - Random breakables - Cube maps all working - Indoors - Windows - AFK killer - Soundscape + some random timed sounds - Fall damage filter - 2 Grenade secret spots > To install the map, put the cstrike folder in the download over the old one and overwrite. Hope you enjoy the map. Put a lot of time in it! Rating, commenting, advising is more then welcome! Enjoy! :D
